[src:problem-details-rfc/list-of-http-status-codes] The server has fulfilled a request for the resource, and the response is a representation of the result of one or more instance-manipulations applied to the current instance.
[src:problem-details-rfc/list-of-http-status-codes] A 3xx status indicates that the client must take additional action, generally URL redirection, to complete the request.
